  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Minsk Group co-chairs, personal representative of chairperson in office and high level planning group: UK statement
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Delivered by Ambassador Neil Bush at the OSCE Permanent Council on 19 November 2020.
</p>

  </div>
</div>

